{"tid":1842931,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被問及封關 陳肇始：要再考慮 正檢視時機","createTime":"2020-01-26T03:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T14:46:56.000Z","uid":212626,"like":17,"dislike":340,"uniUserReply":118,"replies":[{"pid":"7dd01ac0570a6263623fbe9b2422c74c687c9dde","tid":1842931,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:45:07.000Z","msg":"對於坊間有意見希望政府封閉關口，食物及衞生局局長陳肇始表示，一定會考慮加強出入口管制，正檢視那個時間做最有效及如何做。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否要內地部門同意才可以加強出入境管制，她說與對方的感受無關，又說要實行涉及內地相關單位的措施，雙方需要協調。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始在一個電視節目又說，在機場和高鐵站試行電子健康申報後，如果沒有問題，便會盡快在不同陸路口岸實施。她說，健康申報有助追蹤緊密接觸者，但有些交通工具沒有座號無法申報，所以實施健康申報的優次不是最高。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始表示，在不同口岸實施健康申報有不同複雜性，加上新年旅客非常多，當局希望做到追蹤緊密接觸者的效用，亦不想在口岸造成阻塞。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504890-20200126.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504890-20200126.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=a23aac0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504890-20200126.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b8da2112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504890-20200126.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"37374af3056c8ab67ab314f7596b75860eec4e6b","tid":1842931,"uid":68598,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:46:06.000Z","msg":"屌佢收皮啦 尋日睇FD張卡寫完冇人理冇人睇"},{"pid":"4da03e1df1264f06a5da45e76294c35a2d986393","tid":1842931,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db32054a2ccc06ea848d1b4f276f2b01c0b25e23","tid":1842931,"uid":90328,"like":92,"dislike":1,"score":91,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:46:43.000Z","msg":"檢視得黎全港都死哂啦 成班高官都弱智"},{"pid":"14258b1b5907e61ac608705a427cd534dafc1a32","tid":1842931,"uid":810,"like":70,"dislike":1,"sc