27bbe70440b33d72cfb538","tid":1842931,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:50:08.000Z","msg":"做酒店既會唔會肯為左封關放棄生意？而係照放佢地黎住，係酒店傳播病毒？<br />\n<br />\n做開中國客保險既，會唔會為左生意而唔幫佢地落香港，避免佢地係社區傳染？<br />\n<br />\n同樣做地產/商場/貿易，會唔會肯犧牲半年既營業額而讚成封關？<br />\n<br />\n唔會，一定唔會，每個人都為左私利賺盡最後一分錢然後走佬。唔理今次疫症為香港社會帶黎幾多人命損失同醫療開支。"},{"pid":"600181db64d4acb15db506cfb9778e3ead514b11","tid":1842931,"uid":252854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:51:19.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 呢條賤種全家死快啲啦"},{"pid":"5bbcc745e3c01f19ac538633a2e3d9abd5085568","tid":1842931,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:51:51.000Z","msg":"唔好比我見到佢戴口罩，佢話唔洗架麻"},{"pid":"d4bfc95fcf59e357d77f72bbdbb922fc5fc2ed4c","tid":1842931,"uid":258328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:57:47.000Z","msg":"等緊個時機係全港罷工"},{"pid":"fc3c48fc7897bf4c5cc5e585813b700deb56880c","tid":1842931,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c4d66c46dd0e3912126dcba8e36d1eb3a97843","tid":1842931,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:03:46.000Z","msg":"政府嘅方針不嬲都係唔死人唔做野"},{"pid":"fcc62ebf835dc4024ea1e722f6877979a910437c","tid":1842931,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:06:32.000Z","msg":"陳笑恥, 最無恥<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bq70aOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBq70aOE.jpg&h=84a3d903&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dedf2baf62eb5e542caed636f8ee0b3e4c97bdfd","tid":1842931,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7014b27289fce2627f610ca451a63be45b0701df","tid":1842931,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dd01ac0570a6263623fbe9b2422c74c687c9dde","tid":1842931,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:45:07.000Z","msg":"對於坊間有意見希望政府封閉關口，食物及衞生局局長陳肇始表示，一定會考慮加強出入口管制，正檢視那個時間做最有效及如何做。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否要內地部門同意才可以加強出入境管制，她說與對方的感受無關，又說要實行涉及內地相關單位的措施，雙方需要協調。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始在一個電視節目又說，在機場和高鐵站試行電子健康申報後，如果沒有問題，便會盡快在不同陸路口岸實施。她說，健康申報有助追蹤緊密接觸者，但有些交通工具沒有座號無法申報，所以實施健康申報的優次不是最高。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始表示，在不同口岸實施健康申報有不同複雜性，加上新年旅客非常多，當局希望做到追蹤緊密接觸者的效用，亦不想在口岸造成阻塞。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504890-20200126.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504890-20200126.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=a23aac0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504890-20200126.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b8da2112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504890-20200126.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"係需要協調一下，等果班中左武肺既支共高官同家人落埋黎香港睇醫生先，大家一家人嘛，而家未係時機喇。"},{"pid":"b480c3383833d3f11dad2af66a1a380f11a773bb","tid":1842931,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8a2e7f6d02bb6aee977563466b94f5b1ec7b419","tid":1842931,"uid":24168,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:47:17.000Z","msg":"時機就係等足夠病人入嚟香港散播"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:11:07.000Z","msg":"特別係某的有錢有關係既友好。要等埋。"},{"pid":"960a81cc2c2d990c3c04414a47d58fb206451bf4","tid":1842931,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"陳笑始：正等第一個人死"},{"pid":"e4f46b530f9917f7f312f05c0f9643298efc2cb3","tid":1842931,"uid":41906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:26:37.000Z","msg":"你地咁樂觀覺得有人死會封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本冇大陸order爆到班高官中